From 3eca5c8bc774c99668bfe2eb05aca942c45ff047 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>
Date: Fri, 23 Jan 2026 01:08:02 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] net: add HPE GXP UMAC ethernet driver

Add ethernet driver for the UMAC controller found on HPE GXP SoCs.
This controller is connected to an external Marvell 88E1415 PHY via an
SGMII interface.

Co-developed-by: Jean-Marie Verdun <jean-marie.verdun@hpe.com>
Signed-off-by: Jean-Marie Verdun <jean-marie.verdun@hpe.com>
Signed-off-by: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>
---
 MAINTAINERS                      |   2 +
 arch/arm/dts/hpe-gxp-u-boot.dtsi |  24 ++
 arch/arm/dts/hpe-gxp.dtsi        |  42 +++
 configs/gxp_defconfig            |   7 +
 drivers/net/Kconfig              |   9 +
 drivers/net/Makefile             |   1 +
 drivers/net/gxp_umac.c           | 585 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 drivers/net/gxp_umac.h           | 137 ++++++++
 8 files changed, 807 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 drivers/net/gxp_umac.c
 create mode 100644 drivers/net/gxp_umac.h

